{"tid":810830,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"PRODUCE48之曺柔理以外參加者後續討論區（133）好羨慕可以用touch遮住____睇VLIVE嘅人","createTime":"2018-09-08T09:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T04:55:44.000Z","uid":204923,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"29715bc62ecbccf5453f04479d0f41c57db65ee2","tid":810830,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/142131_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F142131_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2ae7cd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裴巴真人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">曹婦與狗不得內進（狗？就係講緊你啊油飯）</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>入黎討論前 請先睇曹柔里既十宗罪<br />\n注：如果唔想受到極大驚嚇建議唔好開自動LOAD圖，你可以選擇逐張㩒以一個循序漸進嘅方式去提高自己嘅接受能力</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">老鼠屎曹柔里</span></strong><br />\nIdol School 時期：<br />\n一、偶校時期出曬名靠扮有情上位<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/03/LH0K2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2FLH0K2f.png&h=0453d0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/03/kQgiIM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2FkQgiIM.png&h=9728723f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二、評價舞台環節 &nbsp;見到有組員0票 大家都被隊友既零分嚇到的時候 佢自己微微的笑左一下 咁岩就比鏡頭影到 反應如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/183734_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F183734_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=b8bbc6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單直接地睇到佢人格<br />\n<br />\npd48 時期：<br />\n三、參加日韓合作節目 開頭仲扮到好nice咁話會幫朱里 但練習時帶住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>慰安婦徽章</strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/000624_79924e6172164ef70f197aa7ff5ab0ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F000624_79924e6172164ef70f197aa7ff5ab0ee.gif&h=80521caf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/000632_7e53c70ccb91bbf76093704c1d393aec.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F000632_7e53c70ccb91bbf76093704c1d393aec.gif&h=ddc9a402&s={SIZE}\" />完全唔尊重日本妹 前期節目花絮入面無見過佢同日本妹交流 就後期淨係識痴住話題性高既nako<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/214800_09b091042d05ef7cccaebdecfe402a40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F214800_09b091042d05ef7cccaebdecfe402a40.jpg&h=ba7f39d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/214800_e8cee1df67f2d333a31daf2cc51e0351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F214800_e8cee1df67f2d333a31daf2cc51e0351.jpg&h=e65214ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四、Position評價明明唱得無羅高恩好 都要爭Main Vocal 最後要成組降key就佢 仲要羅高恩教返佢點唱<br />\n五、第二次排名公佈 喊到要喊出聲先有人知佢喊緊 但一滴眼淚都無 虛偽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/210754_24793cdc7720db9b1be5d22d83b1fe86.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F210754_24793cdc7720db9b1be5d22d83b1fe86.gif&h=53022010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六、Concept評價開頭話想換歌 但之後踢人走又跪哂地話想留低唔唱main vocal都得 留低之後又搶過<br />\n七、傾踢邊個走期間無啦啦唱1000% 同公司狗竹都忍唔住串佢話歌詞都背好 暗指某婦係咪準備好過去<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/PPjzyVCd6CLyUxeMeJ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FPPjzyVCd6CLyUxeMeJ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=cdaafd79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八、最後排名公佈 上次18名升到第3名 扮驚訝 扮感動 但一滴眼淚都無 睇下同樣情況既安有真 金珉周同金彩元 反應差天共地 有d腦既都會睇得出 <br />\n<br />\n以下係某婦同AJY嘅完美配合<br />\n九、Final揀位 瘋狂比人踢走 大大聲講無野話唔緊要 下一個shot即刻播海允比人踢完喊 成功營造天使image<br />\n十、Final首歌降key唱 soyou仲要讚佢 明明降key其他人都唱到 AJY捧佢捧到出哂面<br />\n<br />\n偶校已經對佢好反感 但今次pd48見佢實力改善咗嘗試接受佢 但佢啲行為愈黎愈虛偽 <br />\nby資深偶校飯 丁丁車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《PRODUCE48之曺柔理以外參加者後續討論區》是韓國Mnet在2018年推出的選拔實境節目《Produce 48》撚鳩參加者同觀眾後，推出的討論區</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/231721_8f8f8fac1626cc739a941db11f242500.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F231721_8f8f8fac1626cc739a941db11f242500.png&h=f1e74d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">食屎啦mnet</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/015719_e19bfb3e43268a37e9f4426908b17288.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F015719_e19bfb3e43268a37e9f4426908b17288.png&h=054e9fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了曹柔理外，所有曾參與《Produce 48》的參加者皆可在此討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發起咗4tune8出道 網上請願<br />\n求其填返資料就可以簽名加入請願行列<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thepetitionsite.com/takeaction/357/511/823/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepetitionsite.com%2Ftakeaction%2F357%2F511%2F823%2F&d=uQwPir3gsIxEKPjvnYVJgdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=63ba7314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thepetitionsite.com/takeaction/357/511/823/</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/213047_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F213047_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=80018862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/213053_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F213053_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3784428a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1571f81b86aea354bbe4a85320ca7ee2c77dceb3","tid":810830,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"第一頁留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02b39ff8712b20614c27d6f769cbedc8b35e196","tid":810830,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1571f81b86aea354bbe4a85320ca7ee2c77dceb3","tid":810830,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"第一頁留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"錯POST啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f980620c9b1ae059f9377e003c5503be283e6f00","tid":810830,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm"},{"pid":"7cd73be3c56b11cac73e5a90e9f1f99b604a4898","tid":810830,"uid":33804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"好慢"},{"pid":"0f15b0bea266890c50d7a662a1de064478fc0d4a","tid":810830,"uid":133223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"135喎清"},{"pid":"ecbc83eed10c007915561ce9c96865c809ca0af7","tid":810830,"uid":197602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"做乜自殘<img src=\"/asset